ALMB 435 4/22
UNITED STATES BANKRUPTCY COURT
MIDDLE DISTRICT OF ALABAMA
TRANSCRIPT REQUEST
Parties may order official, typewritten transcripts of the U. S. Bankruptcy Court's proceedings by
completing the following request form.
When we receive your request, we will forward it and the audio recording to the transcriber. The
transcriber must receive payment before the transcript will be processed. Do not send money to the court.
In addition to the estimated number of transcribed pages, the type of transcript (ordinary, 14-day, or
expedited), determines the estimated cost. The estimated cost is only an estimate, and the requester will be
billed for any balance due. A refund will be issued for overpayment. If you have further questions, please
contact the clerk's office at (334) 954-3800 and ask to speak to one of our electronic court reporters.
Type Delivery Cost
Ordinary 30 Days $4.55 per page
14-Day 15 Days $5.15 per page
Expedited 7 Days $5.75 per page
